
editor:
	- select, copy, cut, paste
	- elipse tool
	- parallel tool
	- zooming
	- gui

agent:
	- auto repath, if no path found (occupant of a target switch is standing)
		- add a flag to navigate that filters segments

rail:
	- placement rules
		- switch limits:
			- the maximum is 4, but it has to be a crossing
			- if any of the segments has a 45 degree angle to another one,
				only 3 are allowed
		- properly check for diagonal neighboring segments

